  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "f7138c1521:1",
      "text": "允许用户将 pattern networks 预计算或 \"bake\" 到 2D texture images 或 3D point clouds 中。",
      "ascii_letters": 45,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "f7138c1521:2",
      "text": "Bake Patterns（烘焙 Patterns）",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "f7138c1521:4",
      "text": "PxrBakeTexture",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "f7138c1521:6",
      "text": "PxrBakePointCloud",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "f7138c1521:7",
      "text": "patterns 到你的 shading network 中，也就是你希望将 network 的该状态 bake 到 texture 或 point cloud 的位置。执行 regular renders 时，这些 patterns 会使用 baked textures；执行 bake renders 时，textures 会被 baked，也就是写入 disk。",
      "ascii_letters": 113,
      "cjk_chars": 38
    },
    {
      "item_id": "f7138c1521:8",
      "text": "Starting a Bake Render（启动 Bake Render）",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "f7138c1521:9",
      "text": "bake render 本质上是一个只有一项 setting 不同的 batch render。它使用 bake Hider，而不是 raytrace Hider。要启动 bake render，只需在 RenderMan menu 中选择 Bake Render，而不是 Batch Render。所有常规的",
      "ascii_letters": 94,
      "cjk_chars": 36
    },
    {
      "item_id": "f7138c1521:10",
      "text": "batch render preferences 批量渲染首选项",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "f7138c1521:11",
      "text": "都会应用到 bake render。baked textures 会写入各个 PxrBakeTexture 或 PxrBakePointCloud patterns 中指定的位置。",
      "ascii_letters": 62,
      "cjk_chars": 17
    }
